{"tid":1562331,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[閪鐵好撚驚?] 港鐵稱風險評估後 明中秋節不提供通宵列車服務","createTime":"2019-09-12T03:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T03:45:41.000Z","uid":13867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2a080b54cf9c972aba61639f04253f0af4e6702f","tid":1562331,"uid":13867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:30:20.000Z","msg":"港鐵近日車站設施屢遭破壞，昨有消息傳出港鐵以安全為由，於明日（13日）中秋節將不會一如以往提供通宵列車服務。港鐵今日發新聞稿，宣佈與政府相關部門檢視近期情況，以及進行風險評估後，決定中秋節當日按正常服務時間提供列車服務，將不會提供通宵列車服務，所有港鐵車站將按平常服務時間關閉，即不會延長服務時間。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵指因應預期上升的乘客量，部分路綫將由下午3時起加密班次，為疏導人流，一些較繁忙的車站亦將實施特別人流管理措施。<br />\n港鐵過往每逢大節日如中秋節、平安夜、除夕及年三十晚都會提供通宵列車服務，今次為港鐵首次取消一貫每年在四個節日晚上提供通宵列車服務。<br />\n<br />\n昨日有報道引述消息指，港鐵擬取消通宵服務是因近日車站遭破壞後，均是利用通宵時段維修，若通宵服務將失去修理設施的緩衝時間，且過往中秋節通宵期間的載客量亦不高，亦以免站內出現聚集大批慶祝中秋節人群，引起安全問題。<br />\n同時有多個網民在明日中秋節發起活動，有市民晚上計劃在獅子山、太平山及南朗山築起人鏈，亦有人在各區公園舉行「BE WATER中秋賞燈晚會」。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190912/60036122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190912%2F60036122&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FWsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=1769182c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190912%2F60036122&h=a35ede08\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190912/60036122</a>"},{"pid":"9559fed080297af04ae9682eb9c137c6966bbc36","tid":1562331,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"60b4a760ec50eb5b6b157e8c5de118e1d59ef94c","tid":1562331,"uid":13479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:36:19.000Z","msg":"車費就識加<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9a3527c4083ad0bc2852fa8bbd460773d78a96","tid":1562331,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:38:43.000Z","msg":"驚太子義士冤魂走曬出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a3c46db93ca5eae88b793c2530d32b7de09369","tid":1562331,"uid":13867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60b4a760ec50eb5b6b157e8c5de118e1d59ef94c","tid":1562331,"uid":13479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:36:19.000Z","msg":"車費就識加<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:45:41.000Z","msg":"閪鐵真係冇撚用，執柒埋佢啦不如。"}]}